WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.540
[Amit Varma]: The philosopher Thomas Nagel once wrote an essay called What is it like to be a bat?

00:00:10.540 --> 00:00:14.960
[Amit Varma]: One of the arguments in that essay was that even if a human could try and imagine what

00:00:14.960 --> 00:00:19.680
[Amit Varma]: it was like to be a bat by taking the bat's point of view, it is impossible to know what

00:00:19.680 --> 00:00:22.600
[Amit Varma]: it is like for a bat to be a bat.

00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:27.620
[Amit Varma]: If you wrote an essay called What is it like to be a woman, men would be in a similar situation.

00:00:27.620 --> 00:00:30.600
[Amit Varma]: Our powers of empathy and imagination can only get us so far.

00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:36.360
[Amit Varma]: We are mostly blind to the many ways in which women have to adapt to live in a world designed

00:00:36.360 --> 00:00:38.200
[Amit Varma]: by men, for men.

00:00:38.200 --> 00:00:42.360
[Amit Varma]: And so much have we normalized this, that even many women take it for granted.

00:00:42.360 --> 00:00:46.840
[Amit Varma]: What is it like to be a woman in a world where hotel rooms don't have latches on the inside,

00:00:46.840 --> 00:00:51.880
[Amit Varma]: where offices don't have enough women's toilets, where workplaces don't account for periods

00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:57.200
[Amit Varma]: or pregnancies, where the men are all raja betas and the women are grocery lists trapped

00:00:57.200 --> 00:01:01.920
[Amit Varma]: in human bodies, as my guest today wrote, where you aren't taken seriously, you are

00:01:01.920 --> 00:01:03.440
[Amit Varma]: interrupted all the time.

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:05.400
[Amit Varma]: And Fufaji is a bigot.

00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:11.240
[Amit Varma]: All these extra layers of life that men just don't have to deal with, they need to be documented.

00:01:11.240 --> 00:01:16.360
[Amit Varma]: Someone needs to write about what it's like to be womaning in India.

00:01:16.360 --> 00:01:20.240
[Amit Varma]: Somebody is.

